*xscreensaver-4.09 (17 Mar 2003)

  28 Apr 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.09.ebuild:
  fix motif problems

  17 Mar 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.09.ebuild:
  version bump

*xscreensaver-4.08 (23 Feb 2003)

  27 Feb 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.08.ebuild:
  Mark stable on alpha

  23 Feb 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.08.ebuild files/digest-xscreensaver-4.08 :
  Bump version and add ~alpha to KEYWORDS

*xscreensaver-4.07 (03 Feb 2003)

  03 Feb 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.07.ebuild
  files/digest-xscreensaver-4.07 :

  Version bump.

*xscreensaver-4.06-r2 (26 Oct 2002)

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
  01 Dec 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  xscreensaver-4.06-r2.ebuild :

  Moved to stable for x86

  30 Oct 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06-r2.ebuild:
  Do not disable xml support specifically, as it then breaks gtk+.

  26 Oct 2002; Maik Schreiber <blizzy@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06-r2.ebuild:
  Remove /usr/share/control-center/capplets/screensaver-properties.desktop.

  26 Oct 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06-r2.ebuild:
  Redo the whole thing not to depend on gtk+-2.0 by default, and enable
  --with-gnome theoretically for gnome-1.4.

*xscreensaver-4.06-r1 (26 Oct 2002)

  26 Oct 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06-r1.ebuild:
  Change "xml" flag to "xml2".  Remove "gnome" USE flag.  Change "gtk" in USE
  to depend on gtk+2, and also add libglade2.  If gtk+ is not in USE, make it
  depend on gdk-pixbuf.  This should close bug #9619.

*xscreensaver-4.06 (24 Oct 2002)

  24 Oct 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06.ebuild:
  Fix the libxml hack to actually work.

  24 Oct 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.06.ebuild,
  files/digest-xscreensaver-4.06: Version bump.

*xscreensaver-4.05-r3 (21 Jul 2002)

  15 Apr 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.05-r3.ebuild:
  fix for xscreensaver for motif only installs. thanks to Jason Howlett
  <howlett@byu.edu> in #18068.

  26 Mar 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.05-r3.ebuild:
  should depend on virtual/motif rather than openmotif

  19 Oct 2002; Calum Selkirk <cselkirk@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.05-r3.ebuild:
  Added ppc to KEYWORDS.

  29 Sep 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> pam.d/xscreensaver: Update
  pam.d file to use system-auth.  Bug #5953.
  
  21 Jul 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> xscreensaver-4.05-r3.ebuild: Dep
  change solves bug 4743

